snippet.title: Void 21 Demo footage - Coming 17th of February 2016
snippet.description:
Hi everyone, We've been hard at work making a demo for Void 21 so you guys can try it out and have fun with it. It's almost ready with us adding the finishing touches now so you guys can enjoy it and we can't wait to hear your feedback.

If you want to support the game, vote for us on steam greenlight http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=613801284

Also check out our website http://void21.com
